entry.title: Russian Occupiers to Move 70,000 From Ukraine's Kherson Area
entry.content: Russian officials in occupied Kherson said they would begin mandatory transfers of tens of thousands of residents from parts of the region, as Ukraine continues its offensive to recapture the south.
